			 Steve Slota 
		 

				


					 
						
					 Steve has a B.A. in writing from Messiah College in Pennsylvania, an MLIS from the University of Pittsburgh, and is currently pursuing a Ph.D. at University of California, Irvine in informatics. He is interested in the study of knowledge infrastructures, information policy, affective technology, engagement and activism. 


					 

				


				

			 
 

